{"tid":2384210,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外界解讀習近平不滿林鄭抗疫表現 董建華唱反調兼擦鞋：習的關心是抗疫優勢","createTime":"2021-01-28T11:55:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T12:24:00.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"40cfdbcfdfce43eee7ee3828d597239d331adae3","tid":2384210,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T11:55:40.000Z","msg":"國家主席習近平在特首林鄭月娥述職時提到，要確保一國兩制實踐行穩致遠，必須始終堅持「愛國者治港」，才能落實全面管治權。全國政協副主席董建華隨即和應，指要「堅持愛國者治港，反中亂港者出局」。外界多指習近平不滿林鄭抗疫表現，但董建華指習近平以「沉着應對」來形容特區政府工作，是對林鄭的管治團隊的肯定。他更大拍馬屁，指有習近平的關心，才是香港抗疫最大優勢。<br />\n<br />\n據中新社報道，董建華指，「港版國安法」實施半年多來，香港實現了大亂之後的大治，「事實告訴我們，只有堅持『愛國者治港』，反中亂港者出局，才是香港長期繁榮穩定的保障，才是『一國兩制』行穩致遠的前提。」<br />\n<br />\n董建華指，香港在一年來面對多方面的多重衝擊，「習主席以『沉着應對』來形容特區政府的工作，這是對林鄭月娥帶領的管治團隊的肯定，更是對其未來工作的鼓勵、鞭策和動力」。<br />\n<br />\n習近平對本港第四波疫情表示很關心和很擔憂，外界普遍解讀是習近平不滿林鄭抗疫表現，但董建華卻有不同解讀，指習近平這番話體現了對香港同胞的關切之情，「習主席特別強調中央政府會採取一切措施，全力支持特區政府抗擊疫情，強調祖國是香港的堅強後盾」。<br />\n<br />\n董建華不忘「擦鞋」，指全世界面對疫情，最主要的20個經濟體去年皆錄得負增長，惟有中國一枝獨秀，「應該承認，僅僅依靠香港自身的努力，無法有效控制病毒的傳播。有習主席的關心和國家的支持，才是香港抗疫最大的政治資本和優勢，也是香港的幸運」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210128/TOTLCRX7LRFB5BKL3E2LUOTUSY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210128%2FTOTLCRX7LRFB5BKL3E2LUOTUSY%2F&d=YX1qj72dVL8lCt3J0nVEUsWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=552e6946\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210128%2FTOTLCRX7LRFB5BKL3E2LUOTUSY%2F&h=b65dd2d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210128/TOTLCRX7LRFB5BKL3E2LUOTUSY/</a>"},{"pid":"5b2c595322069ad584b4377c617b5c0d60344a08","tid":2384210,"uid":6435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T11:58:32.000Z","msg":"知道老懵董咁講就知一定開反面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3078b5e53f2336d74970532e0a5d642d2574187b","tid":2384210,"uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T12:02:18.000Z","msg":"林生 ： 屌你老母，要我帶底褲口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4093ce977fcf6323d80717de9f010bdff0de7c88","tid":2384210,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T12:03:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc8a800e56f08e51a2394d207ba8b62c29eb626a","tid":2384210,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T12:06:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4b89a80be779059ae960c8c0d9ba81f0c9f61c","tid":2384210,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3078b5e53f2336d74970532e0a5d642d2574187b","tid":2384210,"uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T12:02:18.000Z","msg":"林生 ： 屌你老母，要我帶底褲口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T12:09:26.000Z","msg":"全部人都係即棄，得果兩條友係底褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aceb23f41845aef5e1a981e8a5